{"tid":2439893,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"唯唯做抗日片男一 冇人講?","createTime":"2021-03-09T14:33:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T15:39:15.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bb5a06b7249a61905ee97230deae8532df03aa7f","tid":2439893,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T14:33:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2021/3/1615285549_wm-1280w.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2021%2F3%2F1615285549_wm-1280w.jpeg&h=60f3d466&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n愛國當然有回報，梁競徽(唯唯)過去時常發表愛國言論，邀他擔任抗日片男主角，絕對有說服力。早前唯唯到橫店拍攝了一部抗日cult片《浴血狂蟒》，他在微博上載照片留言道︰「是日拍攝完成～回去梳洗～非常開心可以參與這次拍攝～中國軍人～就是牛！保家衛國！這是我們的使命。」而預告片段亦已可在抖音中看到。<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2021/3/1615285545_C8-1280w.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2021%2F3%2F1615285545_C8-1280w.jpeg&h=e43dfeb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據網上資料顯示，此片以1945年發生的緬北滇西反攻戰為背景，故事提到中國應英方要求，派了一支遠征軍入緬對抗日軍。戰鬥中，有三架飛虎隊戰機被日軍擊落在雲南原始森林大娘山中，而日本研究的生化武器在叢林中泄露，導致一條巨蟒變異，劇情相當離奇。<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2021/3/1615285535_Gv-1280w.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2021%2F3%2F1615285535_Gv-1280w.jpeg&h=5dba5a75&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2021/3/1615285538_NK-1280w.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2021%2F3%2F1615285538_NK-1280w.jpeg&h=43c3489d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2021/3/1615285531_Ub-1280w.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2021%2F3%2F1615285531_Ub-1280w.jpeg&h=f98b6ca2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b13bf45b91267f9c3e2094e5d5861d3b5c35c1e","tid":2439893,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T14:43:27.000Z","msg":"要手撕日本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n定係手槍打飛機"},{"pid":"30fcd1be59c714b99e1f861415385ec26654b58b","tid":2439893,"uid":211461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:06:19.000Z","msg":"入緬國軍美械師<br />\n半個民國軍徽都睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67c9e006e98d65299074baa1289e1db7bb663653","tid":2439893,"uid":38301,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:23:56.000Z","msg":"無人講咪唔好講囉DNLM<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"368d77d18664023a78ed8445ee2795eb9f49efec","tid":2439893,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67c9e006e98d65299074baa1289e1db7bb663653","tid":2439893,"uid":38301,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:23:56.000Z","msg":"無人講咪唔好講囉DNLM<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:26:26.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"b6a04dc4aa860db459f18c96c3e6e12a7811b5d1","tid":2439893,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:31:52.000Z","msg":"呢條撚樣唔係咁俾佢彈起紅嘛"},{"pid":"303393feba1612e34a2d06186357813cde12c795","tid":2439893,"uid":84588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:39:15.000Z","msg":"得啦，唯萎咁都紅唔起就不如死左佢，浴血狂蟒之災呢套聽個名都知係大片來啦"}]}